10#include <stdio.h>
11#include "internal/cryptlib.h"
12#include <openssl/conf.h>
13#include <openssl/asn1.h>
14#include <openssl/asn1t.h>
15#include <openssl/x509v3.h>
16
17ASN1_SEQUENCE(AUTHORITY_KEYID) = {
18 ASN1_IMP_OPT(AUTHORITY_KEYID, keyid, ASN1_OCTET_STRING, 0),
19 ASN1_IMP_SEQUENCE_OF_OPT(AUTHORITY_KEYID, issuer, GENERAL_NAME, 1),
20 ASN1_IMP_OPT(AUTHORITY_KEYID, serial, ASN1_INTEGER, 2)
21} ASN1_SEQUENCE_END(AUTHORITY_KEYID)
22
23IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS(AUTHORITY_KEYID)
